metadata.name: Notifications GET /api/v1/notifications with account_id param returns only notifications from specified user

sql_query.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM "oauth_access_tokens" WHERE "oauth_access_tokens"."token" = $1 LIMIT $2
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "oauth_access_tokens" WHERE "oauth_access_tokens"."token" = $1 AND "oauth_access_tokens"."id" != $2 LIMIT $3

SELECT "notifications".* FROM "notifications" INNER JOIN "accounts" ON "accounts"."id" = "notifications"."from_account_id" WHERE "notifications"."account_id" = $1 AND "accounts"."suspended_at" IS NULL AND "notifications"."from_account_id" = $2 ORDER BY "notifications"."id" DESC LIMIT $3
SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."id" = $1 ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC LIMIT $2
SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."id" = $1 ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC
SELECT "media_attachments".* FROM "media_attachments" WHERE "media_attachments"."status_id" = $1 ORDER BY "media_attachments"."id" ASC
